>Description:
Running this program 

#lang racket

(require redex)

(define-language L 
  (e 1 2 3))

(define ->l
  (reduction-relation
   L
   (--> (e_1 ..._c 3 e_2 ..._c) (e_1 ... 3 2 e_2 ..._c))))

yields this error message: 

term: before underscore must be either a non-terminal or a built-in pattern in: ..._c

But e_2 obviously is a pattern/non-terminal. 
