 Is this really a wording issue? The mistake is that ..._c shows up on =
 the RHS. If ..._c can never show up on the RHS, then I would raise an =
 error that says "indexed ... cannot appear on the RHS" or something like =
 that. If they can, I am actually stumped.=20
 
 
