 1. A general error message would be "An indexed ellipsis is not allowed =
 in this (kind of) term context." This would work well if you could =
 highlight the specific ellipsis that is in error.=20
 
 2. Can you grab enough of the context to make the error message more =
 specific? In that case, you could specialize the error message w/o =
 spending energy on highlighting the specific ellipsis.=20
 
 -- Matthias
 
 
 
